   ON END-KEY UNDO MAIN-BLOCK, LEAVE MAIN-BLOCK:

  RUN setup-ui.

  DYNAMIC-FUNCTION("center-frame":U IN _h_func_lib, FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}:HANDLE).
